      "amount": "1/4 tsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "chicken or vegetable broth",
      "amount": "2 tbsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and grated ginger, sautéing for about 1 minute until fragrant but not browned.",
    "Stir in bell peppers, zucchini, green beans, mascarpone, heavy cream, broth, salt, pepper, and paprika. Mix well to combine ingredients.",
    "Cook for an additional 5-7 minutes, stirring occasionally until vegetables are tender and sauce is thickened slightly.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or over gluten-free pasta."
